\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {4.2}{\ignorespaces End-to-end pipeline flow of TruthfulRAG v5 (landscape view). Eight stages — \emph  {Corpus Ingestion} [A1/N1/N4/N5], \emph  {Hybrid Retrieval} [BM25+Semantic], \emph  {Query Processing} [B4/C7], \emph  {Scoring} [N2], \emph  {Conflict Resolution} [SAFE\_FOR elimination], \emph  {Adaptive Entropy Filter} [auto-keep], \emph  {Confidence Calculation}, and \emph  {Final Answer} — are shown with their decision logic and inter-stage data flows. Function identifiers in brackets correspond to the implementation in Chapter~5.}}{16}{figure.caption.12}\protected@file@percent }
