\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {4.6}{\ignorespaces State transition diagram for TruthfulRAG v5. Normal execution cycles: \textsc  {Idle} $\to $ \textsc  {Ingesting} $\to $ \textsc  {Ready} $\to $ \textsc  {Retrieving} $\to $ \textsc  {Resolving} $\to $ \textsc  {Generating} $\to $ \textsc  {Ready}. Any runtime error transitions the system to \textsc  {Error}; a process restart resets it to \textsc  {Idle}.}}{20}{figure.caption.16}\protected@file@percent }
